  <summary date="2024-01-26T14:48:27Z" status="Introduced in House">Billionaire Minimum Income Tax Act

This bill imposes a minimum tax on individual taxpayers whose net worth for the taxable year exceeds $100 million. The tax is equal to 25% of the sum of a taxpayer's taxable income, plus net unrealized gains for the taxable year. The tax may not exceed 40% of the amount by which the taxpayer's net worth exceeds $100 million.</summary>
